<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/929794-this-book-was-attacked-as-a-lot-of">This book was attacked as a lot of speculation and misreadings. But where are the books which tell the real story? I mean what are the books that have a different view on the same subject, if there are any? Having read this I would like to read those to have the other side of the argument.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_929794'><a id="like_count_community_question_929794" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/929794?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F606818.Holy_Blood_Holy_Grail">like</a></span>

</li>
